  "texts": [
    "As illustrated in Figure 7b, responses generated without accompanying explanations tend to include some non-existent answers.",
    "While this might impair overall performance, prioritizing the provision of explanations before answers is essential for augmenting the model's capacity for deductive reasoning through the questions.",
    "We further assessed the reasoning capabilities of LLMs by examining the congruence in accuracy distribution between human cohorts and LLMs, as depicted in Figures 5c and 5d.",
    "For the correlation computation, we initially subtracted the mean value to mitigate bias stemming from the correct answer target.",
    "Incorporating explanations into LLM responses seemingly augments their resemblance to human-like attributes."
  ],
